<p>'We are just kind of in a holding pattern like the rest of the world. So, again, it's just something we have to wait and see in a few months how this all pans out.'</p>

<p>Later that month, Alex told Jimmy Fallon that everything was a little more 'fluid' when it comes to planning their big day.</p>

